 5			Relative Humidity            Percent                  999.0
 6			U Wind Component             Meters/Second            999.0
 7			V Wind Component  	     Meters/Second            999.0
 8			Wind Speed		     Meters/Second	      999.0
 9			Wind Direction		     Degrees		      999.0
