 11			Longitude		     Degrees		      999.0
 12			Latitude		     Degrees		      999.0
 13		        Range			     Kilometers               999.0	
 14			Angle			     Degrees		      999.0
 15 			Altitude		     Meters		    99999.0
 16			QC flag for Pressure                                   99.0
 17			QC flag for Temp				       99.0
